The '''Great Temple''' was a building on the planet [[Lorahns/Legends|Lorahns]] that was the center of the [[Order of the Ffib|Ffib]] religion.

[[File:GrandTemple.jpg|thumb|left|150px|Reess Kairn devastates the Ffib temple.]]
During the time of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]]-turned-[[Pirate/Legends|pirate]], [[Reess Kairn]], ransacked the Great Temple&mdash;destroying sacred texts, stealing priceless artifacts, and murdering four Ffib priests during his getaway. This was a major factor in contributing to the Ffib's [[Anti-Jedi sentiment/Legends|hatred of the Jedi]].

